📌 Instructions

All project files are included in this repository.

This project uses PHP, so make sure you have XAMPP installed and running (Apache & MySQL).
The SQL file is provided inside the backend folder — import it using phpMyAdmin.
Place the project folder inside your htdocs directory and name it budgetflow_api.

Start Apache and MySQL in XAMPP, then run the project in your browser:

http://localhost/budgetflow_api
⚙️ Setup Steps
Install and open XAMPP
Start Apache and MySQL
Import the database from the backend folder
Move and rename the project folder to budgetflow_api inside htdocs
Open in browser and you're good to go

